  "- Install Thunderbird addons: Minimize to Tray, Lightning, add email accounts \n" \
  "- Run Webstorm: /opt/webstorm/bin/webstorm.sh \n" \
  "- \n" \
  "- \n" \
  "- \n" \
  "- \n"   \
  "${white}";
